#: src/netedit/GNETagPropertiesDatabase.cpp:6880
msgid ""
"Minimum distance to pedestrians that are walking towards the conflict point "
"with the ego vehicle."
msgstr ""
"Jarak minimum ke pejalan kaki yang berjalan menuju titik konflik dengan "
"kendaraan ego."

#: src/netedit/GNETagPropertiesDatabase.cpp:6886
msgid ""
"The accumulated waiting time after which a vehicle will drive onto an "
"intersection even though this might cause jamming."
msgstr ""
"Waktu tunggu terakumulasi setelah kendaraan akan memasuki persimpangan "
"meskipun hal ini dapat menyebabkan kemacetan."

#: src/netedit/GNETagPropertiesDatabase.cpp:6892
msgid ""
"This value causes vehicles to violate a yellow light if the duration of the "
"yellow phase is lower than the given threshold."
msgstr ""
"Nilai ini menyebabkan kendaraan melanggar lampu kuning jika durasi fase "
"kuning lebih rendah dari ambang batas yang diberikan."

#: src/netedit/GNETagPropertiesDatabase.cpp:6898
msgid ""
"This value causes vehicles to violate a red light if the duration of the red "
"phase is lower than the given threshold."
msgstr ""
"Nilai ini menyebabkan kendaraan melanggar lampu merah jika durasi fase merah "
"lebih rendah dari ambang batas yang diberikan."

#: src/netedit/GNETagPropertiesDatabase.cpp:6904
msgid ""
"This value causes vehicles affected by jmDriveAfterRedTime to slow down when "
"violating a red light."
msgstr ""
"Nilai ini menyebabkan kendaraan yang terpengaruh oleh jmDriveAfterRedTime "
"melambat saat melanggar lampu merah."

#: src/netedit/GNETagPropertiesDatabase.cpp:6910
msgid ""
"This value causes vehicles to ignore foe vehicles that have right-of-way "
"with the given probability."
msgstr ""
"Nilai ini menyebabkan kendaraan mengabaikan kendaraan lawan yang memiliki "
"hak jalan dengan probabilitas yang diberikan."

#: src/netedit/GNETagPropertiesDatabase.cpp:6916
msgid "This value is used in conjunction with jmIgnoreFoeProb."
msgstr "Nilai ini digunakan bersama dengan jmIgnoreFoeProb."

#: src/netedit/GNETagPropertiesDatabase.cpp:6917
msgid ""
"Only vehicles with a speed below or equal to the given value may be ignored."
msgstr ""
"Hanya kendaraan dengan kecepatan di bawah atau sama dengan nilai yang "
"diberikan yang dapat diabaikan."

#: src/netedit/GNETagPropertiesDatabase.cpp:6923
msgid ""
"This value configures driving imperfection (dawdling) while passing a minor "
"link."
msgstr ""
"Nilai ini mengonfigurasi ketidaksempurnaan mengemudi (dawdling) saat "
"melewati tautan minor."

#: src/netedit/GNETagPropertiesDatabase.cpp:6929
msgid ""
"This value defines the minimum time gap when passing ahead of a prioritized "
"vehicle. "
msgstr ""
"Nilai ini mendefinisikan jarak waktu minimum saat melewati di depan "
"kendaraan yang diprioritaskan. "

#: src/netedit/GNETagPropertiesDatabase.cpp:6935
msgid "Willingess of drivers to impede vehicles with higher priority"
msgstr ""
"Kesediaan pengemudi untuk menghalangi kendaraan dengan prioritas lebih tinggi"

#: src/netedit/GNETagPropertiesDatabase.cpp:6946
msgid ""
"The eagerness for performing strategic lane changing. Higher values result "
"in earlier lane-changing."
msgstr ""
"Keinginan untuk melakukan pergantian lajur strategis. Nilai lebih tinggi "
"menghasilkan pergantian lajur lebih awal."

#: src/netedit/GNETagPropertiesDatabase.cpp:6952
msgid ""
"The willingness for performing cooperative lane changing. Lower values "
"result in reduced cooperation."
msgstr ""
"Kesediaan untuk melakukan pergantian lajur kooperatif. Nilai lebih rendah "
"menghasilkan kerja sama yang berkurang."

#: src/netedit/GNETagPropertiesDatabase.cpp:6958
msgid ""
"The eagerness for performing lane changing to gain speed. Higher values "
"result in more lane-changing."
msgstr ""
"Keinginan untuk melakukan pergantian lajur demi menambah kecepatan. Nilai "
"lebih tinggi menghasilkan lebih banyak pergantian lajur."

#: src/netedit/GNETagPropertiesDatabase.cpp:6964
msgid ""
"The eagerness for following the obligation to keep right. Higher values "
"result in earlier lane-changing."
msgstr ""
"Keinginan untuk mengikuti kewajiban menjaga kanan. Nilai lebih tinggi "
"menghasilkan pergantian lajur lebih awal."

#: src/netedit/GNETagPropertiesDatabase.cpp:6970
msgid ""
"The eagerness for using the configured lateral alignment within the lane."
msgstr ""
"Keinginan untuk menggunakan penyelarasan lateral yang dikonfigurasi dalam "
"lajur."

#: src/netedit/GNETagPropertiesDatabase.cpp:6971
msgid ""
"Higher values result in increased willingness to sacrifice speed for "
"alignment."
msgstr ""
"Nilai lebih tinggi menghasilkan peningkatan kesediaan untuk mengorbankan "
"kecepatan demi penyelarasan."

#: src/netedit/GNETagPropertiesDatabase.cpp:6977
msgid ""
"The eagerness for overtaking through the opposite-direction lane. Higher "
"values result in more lane-changing."
msgstr ""
"Keinginan untuk mendahului melalui lajur arah berlawanan. Nilai lebih tinggi "
"menghasilkan lebih banyak pergantian lajur."

#: src/netedit/GNETagPropertiesDatabase.cpp:6983
msgid "Willingness to encroach laterally on other drivers."
msgstr "Kesediaan untuk menyerobot secara lateral ke pengemudi lain."

#: src/netedit/GNETagPropertiesDatabase.cpp:6989
msgid ""
"Minimum lateral gap when encroaching laterally on other drives (alternative "
"way to define lcPushy)"
msgstr ""
"Jarak lateral minimum saat menyerobot secara lateral ke pengemudi lain (cara "
"alternatif untuk mendefinisikan lcPushy)"

#: src/netedit/GNETagPropertiesDatabase.cpp:6995
msgid "Willingness to accept lower front and rear gaps on the target lane."
msgstr ""
"Kesediaan untuk menerima jarak depan dan belakang yang lebih kecil pada "
"lajur target."

#: src/netedit/GNETagPropertiesDatabase.cpp:7001
msgid "Dynamic factor for modifying lcAssertive and lcPushy."
msgstr "Faktor dinamis untuk memodifikasi lcAssertive dan lcPushy."

#: src/netedit/GNETagPropertiesDatabase.cpp:7007
msgid ""
"Time to reach maximum impatience (of 1). Impatience grows whenever a lane-"
"change manoeuvre is blocked."
msgstr ""
"Waktu untuk mencapai ketidaksabaran maksimum (sebesar 1). Ketidaksabaran "
"meningkat setiap kali manuver pergantian lajur diblokir."

#: src/netedit/GNETagPropertiesDatabase.cpp:7013
msgid "Maximum lateral acceleration per second."
msgstr "Percepatan lateral maksimum per detik."

#: src/netedit/GNETagPropertiesDatabase.cpp:7019
msgid ""
"Factor for configuring the strategic lookahead distance when a change to the "
"left is necessary (relative to right lookahead)."
msgstr ""
"Faktor untuk mengonfigurasi jarak pandang strategis saat pergantian ke kiri "
"diperlukan (relatif terhadap pandangan ke kanan)."

#: src/netedit/GNETagPropertiesDatabase.cpp:7025
msgid ""
"Factor for configuring the threshold asymmetry when changing to the left or "
"to the right for speed gain."
msgstr ""
"Faktor untuk mengonfigurasi asimetri ambang batas saat berganti ke kiri atau "
"ke kanan demi keuntungan kecepatan."

#: src/netedit/GNETagPropertiesDatabase.cpp:7031
msgid "Upper bound on lateral speed when standing."
msgstr "Batas atas kecepatan lateral saat berhenti."

#: src/netedit/GNETagPropertiesDatabase.cpp:7037
msgid ""
"Upper bound on lateral speed while moving computed as lcMaxSpeedLatStanding "
"+ lcMaxSpeedLatFactor * getSpeed()"
msgstr ""
"Batas atas kecepatan lateral saat bergerak yang dihitung sebagai "
"lcMaxSpeedLatStanding + lcMaxSpeedLatFactor * getSpeed()"

#: src/netedit/GNETagPropertiesDatabase.cpp:7043
msgid ""
"Distance to an upcoming turn on the vehicles route, below which the alignment"
msgstr ""
"Jarak ke belokan mendatang pada rute kendaraan, di bawahnya penyelarasan"

#: src/netedit/GNETagPropertiesDatabase.cpp:7044
msgid "should be dynamically adapted to match the turn direction."
msgstr "harus disesuaikan secara dinamis untuk mencocokkan arah belokan."

#: src/netedit/GNETagPropertiesDatabase.cpp:7050
msgid "The probability for violating rules gainst overtaking on the right."
msgstr ""
"Probabilitas untuk melanggar aturan larangan mendahului di sebelah kanan."

#: src/netedit/GNETagPropertiesDatabase.cpp:7056
msgid "Time threshold for the willingness to change right."
msgstr "Ambang batas waktu untuk kesediaan berganti ke kanan."

#: src/netedit/GNETagPropertiesDatabase.cpp:7062
msgid ""
"Speed difference factor for the eagerness of overtaking a neighbor vehicle "
"before changing lanes (threshold = factor*speedlimit)."
msgstr ""
"Faktor perbedaan kecepatan untuk keinginan mendahului kendaraan tetangga "
"sebelum berganti lajur (ambang batas = faktor*batas kecepatan)."

